data.name: ایمن سبز
data.description: ImanSabz is an established and registered International Import, Export, Trading& Distribution Chemical Company Headquartered in Tehran – Iran. Since 2006 ImanSabz has been involved in Chemical engineering products, Paints, Pigments, Resin, Adhesive, Printing, Oil, Gas & Petrochemicals, Aviation, Tiles, Wax, Food & Beverage, Pharmaceutical Industry and other manufactured Chemical products and Raw Materials.
